lyrics:
[Verse]
I can't escape this feeling inside
The weight on my chest, I can't abide
Darkness surrounds, it's hard to breathe
Losing my grip, I'm begging for reprieve

[Chorus]
I want to fade away, like stars at night
Lost in the shadows, out of sight
Aching for release, my screams unheard
In this broken world, I long to be interred
